<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
     This page lists all the animated, automated <b>Music Machines</b>
that can be seen and/or heard in the
<a href="http://www.houseontherock.com/"><b>House on the Rock</b></a>
(<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/House_on_the_Rock"><b>Wikipedia</b></a>)
Attraction located on Highway 23 between Dodgeville and Spring Green, WI. 
They are listed in the order they are found in the Tour of the House and
other buildings on the grounds.  So you can tell where you are in the
Tour, included are all musical instruments of any kind (#1-42), and all
non-musical machines (#A-I) which require tokens.  Tokens can be purchased
at numerous locations along the Tour at four for $1.00.  Quarters cannot
be used to play the machines, only tokens.  Unused tokens can be redeemed
or spent in the Gift Shop at the end of the Tour.
</p><p>
