&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    ** = It is unknown exactly which instruments throughout the House are
actually being played while you are there, and which have been recorded
and are only played through hidden speakers.  These music machines are
primarily show pieces.  They are not carefully maintained in any way on an
ongoing basis in order to retain their original fully in tune playable
condition.  For example, note especially the pedal harp
<a href="#MusicofYesterday">(#17)</a>.  It looks
like it was pulled out a land fill, just dusted off, and put on display.
